Morbid Crucifixion - Decaying Human Flesh [Metal] (2014) (mp3)

Morbid Crucifixion is a Satanic Slamming Brutal Death project band, formed by one man. The main idea, was to combine satanic lyrical themes in Brutal Death Metal music, & create something unique & original. The bands style changed & it is influenced by the slamming brutality style with sick growls. The bands origin is from Haifa, Israel. Due to lack of brutality music in the era, the project was formed in 2009, & was hoping to give some new brutal tunes to today's underground Brutal death Metal scene worldwide.
